text: Walther Meienreis (born 1877, date of death unknown) was a German fencer. He competed in the individual épée and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1877 births Category:Year of death missing Category:German male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Germany Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
